<plot>Interview of a marine infantryman who has recently returned from a year on the front lines in Iraq, including in Nasariyah, Iraq. The marine discusses one of the most divisive topics in today's society. One soldier's experiences, with an ending that affects people on either side of the issue. Special thanks to LCpl. David Gardner Weimortz who recently re-deployed for a third tour in Iraq.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?413460</url></doc>
